    "name": {
      "zh": "柯尔特 RO991 9x19毫米冲锋枪",
      "en": "Colt RO991 9x19 submachine gun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "RO991",
      "en": "RO991"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "RO991是一款具备射击模式选择能力、发射9×19mm帕弹的冲锋枪，其附带的RIS皮卡汀尼导轨系统由平顶上机匣上和环绕在枪管周围的导轨部分组成，使得其能容易的加装任何战术设备。默认款式为10.3英寸枪管并装备第三代可调节后托。",
      "en": "The RO991 is a compact 9x19 submachine gun combining classic Colt reliability with modern tactical handling capable of delivering controllable automatic fire and reliable suppression in close-quarters combat."
    },
